qDef.qDef:
Pick(
$(v_Selected_Measure_MT_KG)
,Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD)
    ,
    Pick
    (
        [%SynHeadersSalesOne]
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
        ,
        (
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
        )	
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])	
        ,
        (
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        )	
        
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])	,
        (
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])
        )
        ,
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
    )
    ,
    Pick
    (
        [%SynHeadersSalesOne]
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
        ,
        (
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
        )	
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])	
        ,
        (
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID_LY)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year_LY)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
        )	
        
        ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])	,
        (
            Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
            -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Forecast'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Forecast MT])
        )
        ,
        Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Budget'}, [Month ID] = , Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Budget MT])
    )
)
,$(v_Switch_Option_KG)
)
